14namespace rx

16QueryMtl::QueryMtl(gl::QueryType type)
17 : QueryImpl(type),
18 mTransformFeedbackPrimitivesDrawn(0),
19 mCachedResult(0),
20 mCachedResultValid(false)
21{}
22
23QueryMtl::~QueryMtl() {}
24
25void QueryMtl::onDestroy(const gl::Context *context)
26{
27 ContextMtl *contextMtl = mtl::GetImpl(context);
28 if (!getAllocatedVisibilityOffsets().empty())
29 {
30 contextMtl->onOcclusionQueryDestroyed(context, this);
31 }
32 mVisibilityResultBuffer = nullptr;
33}
34
35angle::Result QueryMtl::begin(const gl::Context *context)
36{
37 mCachedResultValid = false;
38 ContextMtl *contextMtl = mtl::GetImpl(context);
39 switch (getType())
40 {
41 case gl::QueryType::AnySamples:
42 case gl::QueryType::AnySamplesConservative:
43 if (!mVisibilityResultBuffer)
44 {
45 // Allocate buffer
46 ANGLE_TRY(mtl::Buffer::MakeBuffer(contextMtl, mtl::kOcclusionQueryResultSize,
47 nullptr, &mVisibilityResultBuffer));
48
49 ANGLE_MTL_OBJC_SCOPE
50 {
51 mVisibilityResultBuffer->get().label =
52 [NSString stringWithFormat:@"QueryMtl=%p", this];
53 }
54 }
55
56 ANGLE_TRY(contextMtl->onOcclusionQueryBegan(context, this));
57 break;
58 case gl::QueryType::TransformFeedbackPrimitivesWritten:
59 mTransformFeedbackPrimitivesDrawn = 0;
60 break;
61 default:
62 UNIMPLEMENTED();
63 break;
64 }
65
66 return angle::Result::Continue;
67}
68angle::Result QueryMtl::end(const gl::Context *context)
69{
70 ContextMtl *contextMtl = mtl::GetImpl(context);
71 switch (getType())
72 {
73 case gl::QueryType::AnySamples:
74 case gl::QueryType::AnySamplesConservative:
75 contextMtl->onOcclusionQueryEnded(context, this);
76 break;
77 case gl::QueryType::TransformFeedbackPrimitivesWritten:
78 {
79 mCachedResult = mTransformFeedbackPrimitivesDrawn;
80
81 // There could be transform feedback in progress, so add the primitives drawn so far
82 // from the current transform feedback object.
83 gl::TransformFeedback *transformFeedback =
84 context->getState().getCurrentTransformFeedback();
85 if (transformFeedback)
86 {
87 mCachedResult += transformFeedback->getPrimitivesDrawn();
88 }
89 mCachedResultValid = true;
90 }
91 break;
92 default:
93 UNIMPLEMENTED();
94 break;
95 }
96 return angle::Result::Continue;
97}
98angle::Result QueryMtl::queryCounter(const gl::Context *context)
99{
100 UNIMPLEMENTED();
101 return angle::Result::Continue;
102}
103
104template <typename T>
105angle::Result QueryMtl::waitAndGetResult(const gl::Context *context, T *params)
106{
107 ASSERT(params);
108 ContextMtl *contextMtl = mtl::GetImpl(context);
109 switch (getType())
110 {
111 case gl::QueryType::AnySamples:
112 case gl::QueryType::AnySamplesConservative:
113 {
114 ASSERT(mVisibilityResultBuffer);
115 if (mVisibilityResultBuffer->hasPendingWorks(contextMtl))
116 {
117 contextMtl->flushCommandBuffer(mtl::NoWait);
118 }
119 // map() will wait for the pending GPU works to finish
120 const uint8_t *visibilityResultBytes = mVisibilityResultBuffer->mapReadOnly(contextMtl);
121 uint64_t queryResult;
122 memcpy(&queryResult, visibilityResultBytes, sizeof(queryResult));
123 mVisibilityResultBuffer->unmap(contextMtl);
124
125 *params = queryResult ? GL_TRUE : GL_FALSE;
126 }
127 break;
128 case gl::QueryType::TransformFeedbackPrimitivesWritten:
129 *params = static_cast<T>(mCachedResult);
130 break;
131 default:
132 UNIMPLEMENTED();
133 break;
134 }
135 return angle::Result::Continue;
136}
137
138angle::Result QueryMtl::isResultAvailable(const gl::Context *context, bool *available)
139{
140 ASSERT(available);
141 ContextMtl *contextMtl = mtl::GetImpl(context);
142 // glGetQueryObjectuiv implicitly flush any pending works related to the query
143 switch (getType())
144 {
145 case gl::QueryType::AnySamples:
146 case gl::QueryType::AnySamplesConservative:
147 ASSERT(mVisibilityResultBuffer);
148 if (mVisibilityResultBuffer->hasPendingWorks(contextMtl))
149 {
150 contextMtl->flushCommandBuffer(mtl::NoWait);
151 }
152
153 *available = !mVisibilityResultBuffer->isBeingUsedByGPU(contextMtl);
154 break;
155 case gl::QueryType::TransformFeedbackPrimitivesWritten:
156 *available = mCachedResultValid;
157 break;
158 default:
159 UNIMPLEMENTED();
160 break;
161 }
162 return angle::Result::Continue;
163}
164
165angle::Result QueryMtl::getResult(const gl::Context *context, GLint *params)
166{
167 return waitAndGetResult(context, params);
168}
169angle::Result QueryMtl::getResult(const gl::Context *context, GLuint *params)
170{
171 return waitAndGetResult(context, params);
172}
173angle::Result QueryMtl::getResult(const gl::Context *context, GLint64 *params)
174{
175 return waitAndGetResult(context, params);
176}
177angle::Result QueryMtl::getResult(const gl::Context *context, GLuint64 *params)
178{
179 return waitAndGetResult(context, params);
180}
181
182void QueryMtl::resetVisibilityResult(ContextMtl *contextMtl)
183{
184 // Occlusion query buffer must be allocated in QueryMtl::begin
185 ASSERT(mVisibilityResultBuffer);
186
187 // Fill the query's buffer with zeros
188 auto blitEncoder = contextMtl->getBlitCommandEncoder();
189 blitEncoder->fillBuffer(mVisibilityResultBuffer, NSMakeRange(0, mtl::kOcclusionQueryResultSize),
190 0);
191 mVisibilityResultBuffer->syncContent(contextMtl, blitEncoder);
192}
193
194void QueryMtl::onTransformFeedbackEnd(GLsizeiptr primitivesDrawn)
195{
196 mTransformFeedbackPrimitivesDrawn += primitivesDrawn;
197}
